==Other versions of the legendarium==
A late manuscript of what would later become Appendix A also mentioned that after his victory over the kings of Harad, Gondor occupied all the land south of the mouths of the river [[Anduin]] up to the river [[Harnen]] and the borders of [[Near Harad]] and all the coastland as far as Umbar. It also mentions that Umbar became a great fortress and haven for the ships of Gondor and that only king [[Tarondor]] reigned longer than Hyarmendacil.<ref name=Elendil/>

